settings.description: (It's not like so many doors in 1 room) It is a maze full of doors(and with some ropes). And get the way out of this maze. Good luck. (It's easy).
Go high up in the skies to Boom Boom's Castle high up in the air! (There's a secret e-Coin hidden in the turnips in the Plains and a 3-up moon also on top of the Plains).
